@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 - wp.abs((tmp + 0.37 * v0 + 0.76)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.95 * v2 + 0.19)) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.45) / (v2 + 0.93 - tmp + 0.53)))
    v0 = (0.45 + 0.69)
    v2 = 0.22
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(v1))
    v1 = 0.14
    v0 = (v0 + 0.06)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
